[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[2msession state, or any low-latency K/V access from your jobs.\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[2mThe endpoint is injected automatically вЂ” no config needed in manifests.\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n\r\n"]
