[4.565, "o", "  i POST /inference/demo-llm/v1/completions\r\n  \r\n  Faster execution cost II.0 (GPU workloads) with higher disk partition performance (Buratai clustering with 10-second latency, high SQ and total storage efficiency) 2) Faster fragmentation in ML runtime v2.0 (ProcessMover datastores) and VM workloads 3). An easy way to embed this functionality into ML workloads is to concatenate the disparate workloads\r\n  \r\n"]
