[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[32mвњ“\u001b(B\u001b[m Inference endpoint deploy, invoke, and teardown\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1mAll of this runs on a single platform, deployed with one command:\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n  \u001b[36mgco stacks deploy-all -y\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[2mRepository: https://github.com/awslabs/global-capacity-orchestrator-on-aws\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[33m\u001b[1mClean up demo jobs?\u001b(B\u001b[m \u001b[2m(y/N)\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n  \u001b[2mSkipping cleanup. Remove jobs manually with:\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n  \u001b[36mkubectl delete jobs --all -n gco-jobs\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mThanks for watching.\u001b(B\u001b[m\r\n\r\n"]
